title: Interpret Function
text: First, $$s(t)=amount$$ of sit-ups someone can do in $$t$$ minutes and $$c(s)=number$$ of calories burned from completing s sit-ups

title: Interpret Composite Function
text: So, reading c(s(3)) from left to right, $$c(s(3))=number$$ of calories burned from the amount of situps done in $$3$$ minutes.
